views.text:
The Green Team are a group of
volunteers from Cambridge Regional
College. These students are currently
studying a course that enables adults
with additional learning needs to
continue their education and gain
experience in the workplace.

Thanks for your hard work Green Team!

Come along and explore the new den-building area near the Woodland Play Area.

views.text: You can find the new den building area near to the Woodland Play Area.
Please be aware that there are sections of uneven ground in the den-building area. For further detailed information please speak to a member of the welcome team.
Please be aware the property closes at 5pm. The Woodland Play area is approximately a 20 minute walk back to the Visitor Centre and car park.
